<:role: ROM Rag_Optimized — Periskopē 認知フロー統合 {#sec_01_overview .periskope .cognition} :>

<:data search_index:
  keywords: periskope, cognition, phi1, phi2, phi3, phi4, phi7, benchmark, ochema, lazy-init, ndcg, entropy, coverage, Φ1-Φ7, の認知ステージを
